tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE reports (
    report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id UUID,
    date DATE,
    impressions INT,
    clicks INT,
    conversions INT
)

CREATE TABLE reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_name TEXT,
    report_date DATE,
    total_impressions INT,
    total_clicks INT
);

CREATE TABLE kpis (
    kpi_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    kpi_name TEXT,
    kpi_description TEXT,
    kpi_formula TEXT,
    target_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget NUMERIC,
    target_audience TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE dashboard_data (
    data_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    dashboard_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    data_date DATE,
    impressions INT,
    clicks INT,
    conversions INT
);

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  report_id INT,
  impressions INT,
  clicks INT,
  conversions INT
);

CREATE TABLE mobile_marketing_campaigns (
    campaign_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    campaign_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_performance_metrics (
    metric_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT REFERENCES mobile_marketing_campaigns(campaign_id),
    date DATE,
    impressions INT,
    clicks INT,
    conversions INT,
    revenue DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE user_engagement (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT REFERENCES mobile_marketing_campaigns(campaign_id),
    date DATE,
    engagement_time INTERVAL,
    interactions INT
);
